/// Mask:          | 1 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 1 | 1 | 0 | 0 | ... | 1 |
/// Bitwise OR  ____________________________________________________
///
/// Result:        | 1 | 1 | 1 | 1 | 1 | 1 | 0 | 0 | ... | 1 |
///
/// In this example, nonces 2, 4, 5 and 251 are invalidated (set to 1); nonces 0, 1, and 3 were
/// already invalidated.


